{"tid":492141,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Cliff Yeung：DSE通識科鼓勵學生罔顧事實　偽裝理性的反教育","createTime":"2017-12-07T08:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T04:38:29.000Z","uid":81554,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bf11b530843499af3db87ebc12bfd281712852c2","tid":492141,"uid":81554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/138680?utm_content=bufferfe36b&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F138680%3Futm_content%3Dbufferfe36b%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=kWCJKjsukCZ1LztrjtSwCv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6add23a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/138680?utm_content=bufferfe36b&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br />\n<br />\n優良的教育應該培養年青人尊重事實，對事物作客觀全面的分析。通識科的課程設計則反其道而行，鼓勵學生罔顧事實，按立場篩選對自己有利的事實。<br />\n<br />\n造成這問題的主要原因，是通識科課程設計強調學生在極廣闊的範疇，就不同議題作出所謂明辨性思考。明辨性思考的要旨是要分辨是非對錯，對於知識和事實有一定的掌握是先決條件。學生涉獵的議題太多，本地、中國、環球的政治、經濟、社會、文化、環境等等都只是蜻蜓點水般略略學一些，學生對知識及事實的掌握必然流於淺薄，在這前提下作所謂明辨性思考，其實是鼓勵學生罔顧事實。<br />\n<br />\n在這樣的課程設計下，學生要在考試取得高分，日常的訓練就是偽裝理性，設法把漠視真理的偽論述弄得看起來很有說服力。這思考方法習以為常，很容易成為思想的一部份，長大了遇到任何問題，慣於以自己的價值觀或對事物的取態作為核心，按自己的立場對事實作出選擇性的處理，有需要時甚至任意演繹或扭曲，對自己立場有利的事實反覆強調，對自己不利的事實則避而不談，再為自己的立場加上一點包裝，以掌握真理的姿態誇誇其談，實際上卻漸漸喪失分別是非的能力，在不知不覺中完全失卻理性而不自知。這是世上最差劣的教育。<br />\n<br />\n睇黎型佬真係對通識科好不滿，有無補緊佢經濟嘅人講吓佢上堂有無屌通識科有幾垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fdb3514ff82854c9c60605e4099d5d795c700b","tid":492141,"uid":141103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:49:46.000Z","msg":"「考評局班人頭豬腦嘅啊嬸呢...」<br />\n聽咗好多次"},{"pid":"e02f2d88c7f25f9033c9fbe6b4c6365296618281","tid":492141,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:49:47.000Z","msg":"佢在考評局做果陣咪就係考評科目主任及評核發展部經理（負責<span style=\"color: red;\">通識科</span>及經濟科）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/beaconcollege.fans/posts/502823369750498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbeaconcollege.fans%2Fposts%2F502823369750498&d=kWCJKjsukCZ1LztrjtSwCv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=84343ba0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/beaconcollege.fans/posts/502823369750498</a><br />\n<br />\n全港唯一 <br />\n唯一曾真正參與新高中課程設計的補習名師，<span style=\"color: red;\">任職科目主任時，曾參與釐訂課程範圍</span>、評分準則及製作試卷樣本，最清楚新高中的考試重點。"},{"pid":"d304b41c1a98b7b8f4c122a79cca600013e120e9","tid":492141,"uid":137166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0944a5d85d28b1ea9f35cb24b61bd7697dcdfdb5","tid":492141,"uid":81554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢在考評局做果陣咪就係考評科目主任及評核發展部經理（負責<span style=\"color: red;\">通識科</span>及經濟科）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/beaconcollege.fans/posts/502823369750498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbeaconcollege.fans%2Fposts%2F502823369750498&d=kWCJKjsukCZ1LztrjtSwCv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=84343ba0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/beaconcollege.fans/posts/502823369750498</a><br />\n<br />\n全港唯一 <br />\n唯一曾真正參與新高中課程設計的補習名師，<span style=\"color: red;\">任職科目主任時，曾參與釐訂課程範圍</span>、評分準則及製作試卷樣本，最清楚新高中的考試重點。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前上佢堂佢好似話想客客氣氣唔想得罪人，同埋話唔係所有嘢都係佢話晒事，唔sure有無記錯"},{"pid":"519d84f3ffbe8893484641aef812d5c26c9e987e","tid":492141,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"當然釐訂一個課程涉及好多人，佢只係其中一部份。<br />\n<br />\n之前通識之父(課程發展議會轄下的通識教育委員會主席)去考都係得level 4<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120721/16534505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120721%2F16534505&d=kWCJKjsukCZ1LztrjtSwCv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=8376f539\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120721%2F16534505&h=0475326b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120721/16534505</a>"},{"pid":"e1d4edabf1d3fb7e549e2341c7e79b2e502523bd","tid":492141,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"AL通識已經笑緊啦，DSE笑得仲勁咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30259b3ef6e9d9edc8dba0f11e09ce02b45b7873","tid":492141,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:13:38.000Z","msg":"應該全面恢復Alevel制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92807b759bbdf1770fce7c111604426cda87e0cc","tid":492141,"uid":23786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:18:13.000Z","msg":"當年AL通識已經勁randomised，棵考可以拎C，mock預A嘅就拎E<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17292b67dc54d6c6919490e05298c9a251e4cfda","tid":492141,"uid":137166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:35:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c49ac2dc26e3380ef94a5f1437a8f21cb6b9257","tid":492141,"uid":137555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:44:23.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔拎理LS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a90c68bcd65b909b6e7df9d0eaa3d2b795f17f","tid":492141,"uid":561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/138680?utm_content=bufferfe36b&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F138680%3Futm_content%3Dbufferfe36b%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=kWCJKjsukCZ1LztrjtSwCv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h